OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying damp
OL,6,Ffor some this evening with patchy rain
OL,7,Fand drizzle. This increasingly
OL,8,Fconfined to higher ground overnight
OL,9,Fand turning dry for many. Remaining
OL,10,Fmurky in some coastal regions with
OL,11,Fmist and hill fog possible. Staying
OL,12,Fbreezy on coasts. Mild.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FCloudy with drizzly rain for
OL,15,Fmany first thing, this persistent over
OL,16,Fhigher ground. Turning brighter from
OL,17,Fthe north through the day with sunny
OL,18,Fspells. Feeling warmer but remaining
OL,19,Fquite blustery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
