OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FPlenty
OL,6,Fof sunshine this weekend and feeling
OL,7,Fmuch warmer with lighter winds. Patchy
OL,8,Flow cloud may affect some coastal
OL,9,Fregions in the west. Perhaps cloudier
OL,10,Fwith isolated showers on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
